Package: cohortTdd.demo
Type: Package
Title: cohortTdd Demo - Cohort Definition Validation Example
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bill", "Baumgartner", email = "william.baumgartner@cuanschutz.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Template project demonstrating cohort definition testing using cohortTdd package.
    Users can replace the sample data files and update test file names to validate their own cohorts.
    Tests cohort logic against synthetic patient data with known inclusion/exclusion patterns.
License: MIT
URL: https://github.com/bill-baumgartner/cohortTdd.demo
BugReports: https://github.com/bill-baumgartner/cohortTdd.demo/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    cohortTdd,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    devtools
